---
import Heartbeat from './Heartbeat.astro';
import TechStack from './TechStack.astro';
---

<section id="city-pulse" class="relative z-20 isolate py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <article>
        <div class="overflow-hidden">
          <h1
            data-reveal="chars"
            data-city-overlap="title"
            class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]"
          >
            CityPulse — The Heartbeat of the City
          </h1>
        </div>

        <p data-reveal="lines" data-city-overlap="meta" class="mt-6 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
          CityPulse is the social app built to help people discover what’s happening right now—right
          where they are. Instead of scrolling through the same feed as everyone else, CityPulse turns
          your city into a living map of moments: places you can visit, vibes you can feel, and pulses you
          can share in real time.
        </p>
        <p data-reveal="lines" data-city-overlap="body" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
          Where traditional social apps tell you what to watch, CityPulse lets the city speak.
        </p>
      </article>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <article>
          <div class="overflow-hidden">
            <h2
              data-reveal="chars"
              data-city-overlap="chars"
              class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]"
            >
              Our Vision
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div
            data-featured-image
            class="mt-7 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md p-6 glass-surface"
          >
            <p data-reveal="lines" data-city-overlap="lines" class="text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
              We believe the best communities don’t just grow online—they grow together, in real life.
              CityPulse is designed to be the heartbeat of the city by making it easier to:
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-4 list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
              <li>find the energy of your neighborhood instantly,</li>
              <li>connect through shared experiences,</li>
              <li>and discover nearby spots before they become “trendy” elsewhere.</li>
            </ul>

            <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
              CityPulse is not about perfection. It’s about presence. Quick, honest updates from people who are actually out there.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <article>
          <div class="overflow-hidden">
            <h2
              data-reveal="chars"
              class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]"
            >
              What CityPulse Does
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div
            data-featured-image
            class="mt-7 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md p-6 glass-surface"
          >
            <p data-reveal="lines" class="text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
              CityPulse blends map + social into one seamless experience:
            </p>

            <div class="mt-10">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <h3 data-reveal="chars" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]">
                  A Map That Feels Alive
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                See pulses across your city—where people are going, what they’re enjoying, and what’s
                popping nearby. CityPulse helps you move through the day with context: not just “what’s nearby,”
                but “what’s worth your time.”
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <h3 data-reveal="chars" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]">
                  A Feed That Matches Your Reality
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                Your feed adapts to how you explore—stories and posts that feel connected to place, not just algorithms.
                Discover vibes from friends, locals, and nearby communities so you always have something to do.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <h3 data-reveal="chars" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]">
                  Stories &amp; Categories That Make Discovery Fast
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                CityPulse makes it easy to recognize the vibe instantly using category-based visuals (Food, Nightlife, Gym, Study, Events, and more). It’s built for speed—so users can scan, tap, and decide in seconds.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <h3 data-reveal="chars" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]">
                  Community Connection (Not Just Broadcasting)
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                CityPulse isn’t only for posting. It’s for engaging—supporting creators, sharing recommendations, and connecting through messages and activity so relationships don’t disappear after the scroll.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <TechStack />
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16">
        <article>
          <div class="overflow-hidden">
            <h2
              data-reveal="chars"
              class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]"
            >
              How It Feels to Use CityPulse
            </h2>
          </div>

          <div
            data-featured-image
            class="mt-7 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md p-6 glass-surface"
          >
            <div class="mt-2 flex justify-center pointer-events-none">
              <Heartbeat />
            </div>

            <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-6 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
              CityPulse is simple at first touch:
            </p>

            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
              <li>Open the app and instantly understand what’s happening nearby.</li>
              <li>Tap a pulse to learn more—then decide if you want to join the moment.</li>
              <li>Share your own pulse to keep the city’s story moving.</li>
              <li>Connect with people who care about the same places and vibes you do.</li>
              <li>It’s “Instagram energy” with “real-world direction”—a social experience that actually helps you live your city.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="mt-10">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <h3 data-reveal="chars" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]">
                  Why CityPulse Exists
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                Most apps fail in one of two ways:
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                <li>They help you discover something, but don’t help you connect.</li>
                <li>They connect people, but ignore the real world around them.</li>
              </ul>
              <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                CityPulse solves that by turning discovery into community. Every post becomes a mini-recommendation, every story becomes a moment you can step into, and every interaction strengthens the local culture that makes cities special.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <h3 data-reveal="chars" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]">
                  The CityPulse Promise
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                CityPulse is built to feel:
              </p>
              <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                <li>Local: connected to neighborhoods and real places.</li>
                <li>Fast: made for quick decisions.</li>
                <li>Authentic: moments over perfection.</li>
                <li>Friendly: a platform where sharing the vibe is encouraged.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-10">
              <div class="overflow-hidden">
                <h3 data-reveal="chars" class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#F5F5F7]">
                  Short About Snippet (for a hero/intro area)
                </h3>
              </div>
              <p data-reveal="lines" class="mt-4 text-[#F5F5F7]/60 leading-relaxed">
                CityPulse is the heartbeat of the city—an app that helps you discover what’s happening nearby through a map-powered social feed. Share quick pulses, explore local vibes by category, and connect with people who are truly part of your community.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

